    {
      "scene_index": 3,
      "label": "第三场",
      "characters_present": [
        "刘备",
        "赵云"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四龙套、四上手、赵云、刘备分上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "久闻大名，如雷贯耳，今日一见，果然名不虚传。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵云",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "赵云有何德能，敢劳使君称赞。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "但不知将军，几时起兵？"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵云",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "即刻起程。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好，将军可命人马前行，你我马上，缓缓而行，以慰平时渴慕。不知赵将军，"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "意下如何？"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵云",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵云",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众将官，人马先行。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（龙套、上手分下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "赵将军，你看当今之时，天下大乱，汉室衰微，众诸侯各据一方，争雄赌胜，"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "日后不知何人成王立帝，重整汉室基业？"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵云",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "想俺赵云，生性蠢笨，乃是草野愚夫，日后成王立帝，是哪一家，使君必有高"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵云",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "见。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "赵将军，备倒想起一人来了：想公孙瓒，乃是汉室功臣，足智有谋，又有赵将"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "军辅助，日后成王霸业，莫非就是此人了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵云",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，使君，想我主公孙瓒，性情高傲，不纳忠言，日后断难成其大事，他只怕"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵云",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不能。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他不能。呵，备又想起一家来了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵云",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是哪一家？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "想那袁术，占据寿春，兵多将勇，又有纪灵、桥藐，勇冠三军，日后或者是此"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "人了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵云",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "想那袁术，优柔寡断，生性矫情，虽有桥藐、纪灵等，皆是一勇之夫，焉能成"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵云",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "其大事？袁术他不能。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他不能。备又想起一人来了：想河北袁绍，四世三公，谋士有田丰、沮受、逢"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "纪、郭图等，武有颜良、文丑之辈，日后汉室基业，定属此人了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵云",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "想那袁绍，昏庸老悖，犹豫多疑，帐下谋士，互相猜忌，自行残害，袁绍他也"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵云",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不能。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "袁绍也不能。备又想起一人来了：想那荆襄王刘表，坐镇荆州，据有长江之险，"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "统属一十三郡，兵精粮足，日后定能称王霸业的了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵云",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那刘表，虽是汉胄，坐镇荆襄，怎奈他无勇无谋，焉能有此大志？刘表他不能。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如此看来，天下竟无人了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵云",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "眼前倒有一人，日后定能成王立帝。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "备倒明白了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵云",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "明白何来？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "想赵将军，英雄盖世，智勇双全，日后天下，定是赵将军的了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵云",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "赵云有何德能，敢设此妄想？刘使君乃是中山靖王之后，汉室宗亲，盖世英雄，"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵云",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "又有关、张辅助，日后天下，定是使君的了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "备乃是困水蛟龙，陷阱猛虎，圣人云：“有美玉于斯，韫匵而藏诸？求善贾而"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "沽诸？沽之哉！我待贾者也。”正是："
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "天上无云难下雨。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵云",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "掌中无剑怎杀人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵云",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "低头不语恨苍穹，"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "刘备身旁少英雄。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵云",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "你好比红日撑空亮，"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "你好比皓月在当空。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘备、赵云同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
